Package: scDEDM
Title: A Discrete Evolutionary Dynamical Model for eGRN Inference from Single-Cell Matched Multi-omics Data
Version: 2.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Taihang", family = "Huang", email = "huangtaihang@buaa.edu.cn", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implements the scDEDM algorithm, a novel method for predicting Enhancer Gene Regulatory Networks (eGRNs) by modeling their discrete evolutionary dynamics along a pseudotemporal trajectory. It is specifically designed for cell-matched single-cell RNA-seq and ATAC-seq data, leveraging the complementary information to infer dynamic regulatory interactions. This package provides a comprehensive toolkit for reconstructing developmental or disease progression pathways from multi-omics snapshots.
